{"tid":2151324,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"等緊世界各地識講中文嘅你入嚟（吹水谷）","createTime":"2020-08-11T10:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T00:28:39.000Z","uid":9178,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"47a40f41a5bc21b4f5cd8cc1cf2019ca756c8181","tid":2151324,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:32:42.000Z","msg":"你係咪覺得好悶阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你係咪覺得生活闊子好窄 想搵下機會識下唔同朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱喇啱喇<br />\n全新群組上線喇 新人唔洗驚融入唔到<br />\n歡迎任何正係想吹水嘅人入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩想講可以講 唔洗驚要出嚟真人面對<br />\n為你嘅WhatsApp 增添熱鬧氣息<br />\n唔驚冇人搵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不論你身在<span class=\"red\">香港/世界各地</span> 只要你識中文<br />\n恭候大家光臨！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自由選擇參與群聚活動<br />\n唔鍾意就唔好入 唔洗講咁多<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/u1YoHXUzpZkXrMSF7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2Fu1YoHXUzpZkXrMSF7&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9Fv%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=c1b9e1fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/u1YoHXUzpZkXrMSF7</a>"},{"pid":"017a27ee8d97235469ff5e325d4cd82162024e9b","tid":2151324,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:54:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31cd90d423b9d97d0e5f0cb4130521ef98d97ee6","tid":2151324,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d761f3c086de85721512bb9d5a0237996f0edd59","tid":2151324,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:10:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa305b0be391830299e99d331c50781e50dd0